The paper deals with facial beauty prediction using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of different computational models and paradigms, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the importance of human perception in facial beauty prediction, which can be related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
